{"tid":1694031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陰公豬】江蘇1.3億元豪宅被指違建要清拆 ，屋主抱頭痛哭　稱自願拆除：支持黨工作","createTime":"2019-11-05T02:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:23:48.000Z","uid":18691,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d614ba555661d7a9f2ffa118c32336dc51b78674","tid":1694031,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2312931668851306?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2312931668851306%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=3beace7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2312931668851306?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇南通一棟<span style=\"color: red;\">造價1.3億元人民幣</span>的超級豪宅，近日被指屬於違法建築，而要夷為平地。屋主聲稱自願配合政府清拆，但就被拍到在屋前與家人抱頭痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n豪宅位於運河邊，一共有三層和地下室，屋內裝修豪華，地下室除了桌球枱還有游泳池，後花園更是種滿綠樹，還有一條景觀河流過。<span style=\"color: red;\">屋主指，豪宅所在地之前是垃圾堆填區，是他自掏錢包把垃圾清走，修路設街燈，再斥資近億元做綠化。</span><br />\n<br />\n為何會在這裏起豪宅？屋主憶述，他在幾年前回鄉探親時，<span style=\"color: red;\">當地村書記勸他留下來投資，對方更向他擔保，可以幫他搞定所有手續</span>。於是他就大灑金錢修橋補路，打地基建豪宅，<span style=\"color: red;\">但就在他建好之際，「政府他說你們要拆，上面政策下來，上面說你違規了。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n於是，村書記的擔保就和1.3億元一起化為烏有。而在清拆的晚上，附近有大批居民來見證，<span style=\"color: red;\">屋主亦主動表示是自願配合政府工作：「這個地方因為是違章的，當時情況我們不懂法，就把它建起來。我相信今天這個地方沒有了，也是正確的，因為我們要支持黨的工作。」不過就在清拆前，屋主曾被拍到和家人在房門前抱頭痛哭。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地政府說，由於房子是違法建築，所以不會有賠償，但他們已經提供很多支持，包括在現場控制秩序。而屋主除了要自毀1.3億元的心血外，還要<span style=\"color: red;\">另外斥資幾十萬請人清拆</span>，他在接受內地傳媒訪問時說：「我把這裡處理完以後，我會去外面做點生意去，因為這個地方的確待不下去了。我現在只想把這裡處理完後，找個清靜地方把戶口遷出去。」<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#豪宅<br />\n#配合黨<br />\n#江蘇<br />\n<br />\nBtw有線中國組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7827c94048eecd8c547a844eefc1782db067556c","tid":1694031,"uid":289978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴熱烈地拆"},{"pid":"ac24b42a42f03c61751cf07a0dbc2f82e40183a9","tid":1694031,"uid":277644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"你還有黨，你愛黨，黨愛你塊地。<br />\n好一個悲慘既愛情故事。"},{"pid":"3ad8c0094945447b955a6c6329336723fc5d0c0a","tid":1694031,"uid":18691,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7827c94048eecd8c547a844eefc1782db067556c","tid":1694031,"uid":289978,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴熱烈地拆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"向上拆 向下拆 一於放任胡亂拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef29f25c68fa7cda21b4ce144f7fe48d5c5b56c","tid":1694031,"uid":18691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"仲要自己出錢拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f517c28a67b7712e893e1cf946f153f8ebb4025d","tid":1694031,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"你還有党"},{"pid":"dde2ee710bc9c5a6c2452a899285cc60549dabd4","tid":1694031,"uid":23951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7ef29f25c68fa7cda21b4ce144f7fe48d5c5b56c","tid":1694031,"uid":18691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"仲要自己出錢拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"死刑都要家屬比返子彈錢啦"},{"pid":"0df0e3ba3b7c3a2523b81b26d07063a51963c9cf","tid":16940