g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb90ca95a6088d8df6e1b4b002f0a9e3cfa12aa","tid":1694031,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1057622ee526f66dd10f19f6cc0902ea3861d964","tid":1694031,"uid":255333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"喺塊垃圾地起屋，千萬成本吹到1.3億，跟住花幾十萬拆咗佢<br />\n<br />\n無限loop，GDP永不破6"},{"pid":"8370d2b3e814b59416ab1f8a6fbc57be2537e3ad","tid":1694031,"uid":47223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"支那人最引以自豪既GBP gogogo"},{"pid":"0a6ae1c39f04333c022b6157845219fd00d51bfa","tid":1694031,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/JzexVA6.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzexVA6.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4a301911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/JzexVA6.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n長期罷工效果<br />\n<br />\n返shift，射波齊參與<br />\n邊日<span style=\"color: red;\">放假</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">射波</span> 就好去遊客旺區振興經濟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊輪住嚟射波<br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"28f9792e644e5a3fc03bf76385eceece36a02913","tid":1694031,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"又谷gdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffc9c3869f0ec7e31db1ce1b3dd8af1846b30e6","tid":1694031,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"屌 同恆基借地比政苦一撚樣 <br />\n前期野做完 地主收返啲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/